==English==

===Noun===
'''rigidity'''

# The quality or state of being [[rigid]]; want of [[pliability]]; the quality of [[resist]]ing change of form; the amount of [[resistance]] with which a body opposes change of form.
# [[stiffness|Stiffness]] of appearance or manner; want of [[ease]] or [[elegance]].

====Antonyms====
*[[flexibility]]
*[[ductility]]
*[[malleability]]
*[[softness]]

